    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The bundle includes two new tanks: Red Pepper and Colorful.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tank comes with unique advantages in battle, such as faster turret rotation and increased overall speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll also get an exclusive set of decorations for the “Masquerade” and “Dead Winter” levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Red Pepper</strong> - is the most powerful tank, leaving fiery trails in its wake. It was designed to ensure nothing stands in your way. No other tank can surpass it in speed. And opponents will only see the fire behind you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826740/extras/005f55b36bafe92946ac1d3dd249f6f3.poster.avif?t=1755267232\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826740/extras/005f55b36bafe92946ac1d3dd249f6f3.webm?t=1755267232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826740/extras/005f55b36bafe92946ac1d3dd249f6f3.mp4?t=1755267232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
